INSTALL

Requirements:
You need to have CodeBlocks installed
If you dont, go here http://www.codeblocks.org/downloads/26

1) Go to "win" project folder
2) Go to "Calculator"
3) Double click the "Calculator.cbp" file
4) This opens up Codeblocks
5) Press "F9" to run the program

If you have the Make utility installed,
1) Go to the win folder
2) You'll see a makefile 
3) Get on any unix-like terminal(You can use cygwin)
4) Type in 'make'
5) The program should compile and output an executable